# ===== 凭证 / token / cookie 一定不入仓 =====
**/cookies*.json
**/cookies_*.json
**/*.cookie
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/secrets.*
**/*token*
**/auth.*

# ===== 临时文件 / 缓存 =====
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/node_modules/

# ===== Skill 工作产物(可重建,不入仓) =====
**/dump/*.html
**/logs/*.log
**/data/*.db
**/data/*.db-journal
**/data/*.db-wal
**/data/*.db-shm
**/.hermes/sessions/

# ===== OS 临时文件 =====
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
